This is a python application which perfoms the following tasks:
    -> Monitoring changes in MongoDB database.
    -> Running a Flask Server for clients to perform following operations:
          ->Subscribing to changes in MongoDB (Particular field Subscriptions also allowed )
          ->To check if client already has any subscription
          ->To update the previous subscription
          ->To delete the subsription.
    ->Running a notification system which fetches changes in MongoDB database and sends email notifications
      to the subscribed clients.
